# 🚀 ReachInbox Onebox Starter Project

## 📘 Overview
This project is a full-stack email categorization and automation system built with:
- **Frontend:** Next.js (TypeScript + React)
- **Backend:** Node.js + Express + TypeScript
- **Database & Search:** Elasticsearch (for indexing and search)

